It was then used generally to express, as here, a previous election or choice as influencing subsequent ones, because the voting of the prmaevoyativa had such a strong in- fluence on the course of the rest of the voting. This influence so often alluded to, was due among other and general causes, such as influence elections nowadays also, to the special religious feeling about omens so strong in the Romans.
